{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10107917133138-3":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10107917133138-3","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100096663019","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096662889","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096683530","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100120068744-10"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":113,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">　　　　　</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">1967年8月23日，苏联宇航员弗拉迪米·科马洛夫驾驶“联盟一号”宇宙飞船在完成太空飞行任务之后，胜利返航。不料，当宇宙飞船返回大气层后，突然发生了恶性事故，减速降落伞无法打开，飞船在两个小时以后将要坠毁。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">苏联中央领导研究后决定：向全国实况转播这次事故。电视台的播音员用沉重的语调宣布：“宇宙飞船发生故障，两个小时后将坠毁，我们将目睹宇航员<span style=\"text-indent: 32px;\">弗拉迪米·</span>科马洛夫殉难。”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">顿时，举国上下被震撼了，人们都沉浸在巨大的悲痛之中。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">在电视上，观众看到了宇航员</span>科马洛夫镇定自若的形象。他面带微笑地对母亲说：“妈妈，您的图像我在这里看得清清楚楚，包括您头上的每根白发。您能看清我吗？”“能，能看清楚。儿啊，妈妈一切都很好，你放心吧！”这时，<span style=\"text-indent: 32px;\">科马洛夫的</span>女儿也出现在电视屏幕上，她只有12岁。科马洛夫说：“女儿，你不要哭。”“我不哭……”女儿已泣不成声，但她强忍悲痛说：“爸爸，你是苏联英雄，我想告诉你，英雄的女儿会像英雄那样生活的！”科马洛夫叮嘱女儿说：“你学习时，要认真对待每一个小数点。联盟一号今天发生的一切，就是因为地面检查时忽略了一个小数点。这场悲剧，也可以叫做对一个小数点疏忽的悲剧。我的孩子，记住它……”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">时间一分一秒地过去了，距离宇宙飞船坠毁只有7分钟了，科马洛夫向全国的电视观众挥挥手说：“同胞们，请允许我在这茫茫的太空与你们告别。”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">这是一次惊心动魄的告别仪式。科马洛夫永远地走了，他留下了对亲人对祖国永恒的爱。但更震撼人们心灵的是，他对女儿说的那番话。他的话警示着人们：对待人生不能有丝毫的马虎，否则，即使是一个细枝末节，也会让你付出沉重的甚至是无法弥补的代价。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><br></p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"下列选项中，最适合作为本文标题的一项是（　）","answers":[{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"小数点的代价","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"伟大的苏联宇航员","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"可以弥补的悲剧","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"<p>从文中找出合适的四字词语填空。</p><p>指面对灾难时冷静的表现。__$$__</p><p>比喻事情或问题的细小而无关紧要的部分。__$$__</p>","answers":[{"answer":"镇定自若","subAnswers":["镇定自若"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100074850748","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"细枝末节","subAnswers":["细枝末节"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":4,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSecon